{"tid":1804154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你地身邊有冇人好鍾意批鬥自己友既人","createTime":"2019-12-30T18:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:06:24.000Z","uid":316410,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc173f22b1dba2a43349784e093e89dce11445ea","tid":1804154,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T18:58:37.000Z","msg":"個運動愈耐 見得愈多<br />\n呢類人又唔係藍 但好多野都屌 <br />\n又屌大部分手足革命小學雞 日程月程表<br />\n生意唔好說喺門口掛句光復香港 etc.<br />\ncomment好多都反諷 <br />\n話樓主因住比人話熱狗 分化撚<br />\n<br />\n雖然有時佢地係有point<br />\n但係佢地既語氣 態度 睇得多其實幾心累<br />\n本身我地呢邊偏弱勢 <br />\n仲要咬自己人多過咬出面人<br />\n真係好懷念運動初期大家勁齊心<br />\n真係有野做唔啱係攞出嚟改善<br />\n而唔係純屌冇建議<br />\n<br />\n睇得多有d攰 發洩下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 唔知係咪焦土派 不過我就好愛香港既"},{"pid":"c38cee7b5b45bd80a2c0a9dbfbc7b9ab08475e73","tid":1804154,"uid":141026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19:04:52.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ea40bf64ce08aee485d91f14c7c409bbe10bdb","tid":1804154,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19:18:08.000Z","msg":"係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818cee0287b14ca762f2f32cc4550f91586bda68","tid":1804154,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19:23:10.000Z","msg":"你剩係睇連登都大把 唔洗身邊 <br />\n從來打自己人係用盡力 仲大力過打狗"},{"pid":"4e7e74983b74ac31bd2a86bc761df98b507f9b08","tid":1804154,"uid":296014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19:23:18.000Z","msg":"上次廿四號同班朋友一齊係彌敦道遊走<br />\n有個朋友係咁屌 話手足唔屌狗咪唔會狗查 話嗌口號好戇鳩 係度咇哩吧啦<br />\n我唔明點解要咁做 真係好撚哽耳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0555c6d4f7b475f744c137d11da5c3d72570c279","tid":1804154,"uid":247719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19